title: Werecat Avenue by Anjela Renee
description:
Gretchen is a Werecat. She lives in Louisiana in the first-ever subdivision just for paranormal's like herself. She meets Adrian at the Night Club where she works, and there is an immediate attraction.

Adrian is the Fae Enforcer, whose job is to capture and apprehend Fae that escape prison. He is sent to capture a Fae named Camilla, but he soon realizes that this isn't just any ordinary job.

Genre: Paranormal Romance
